title: They Sent An Exclusive Smartphone...
description: FULL DETAILS BELOW   The Huawei P10 and P10 Plus are the latest smartphones from Huawei. It comes in a variety of colors including the vibrant blue displayed in this video. It features a dual-lens camera system similar to the Huawei P9 enabling various effects including a shallow depth-of-field mode. It also features upgraded internal specs for a snappier user experience.  More info on the Huawei P10 here -   Thanks to Huawei for sending over the P10 early!
